  <summary date="2020-03-27T14:33:16Z" status="Introduced in House">Federal Firefighter Pay Equity Act 

This bill adjusts the method of determining the average pay of a federal firefighter by adding one-half of a firefighter's basic hourly rate multiplied by the number of overtime hours included as part of&#160;such firefighter's regular tour of duty&#160;for purposes of computing retirement and annuity benefits.</summary>
